Package com.storytron.test Description

Provides implementation for tests.

These are the things being tested:

  • Cloning Deikto, DeiktoTest#testCloneDeiktoState().
  • Loading and saving Deikto preserves its state, DeiktoTest#testDeiktoInputStream().
  • Saving and loading the engine state preserves it, DeiktoTest#testSaveEngineState().
  • Storyworld reference counter is 0 after all players have logout, JanusDeiktoListTest#testJanusDeiktoList().
  • Stress test for janus (reports average reaction time when multiple player run BoP2K), JanusStressTest#main(String[]).
  • Tests for actor editor, SwatTest#testActorEditor().
  • Tests for copyrights editor, SwatTest#testCopyrightEditing().
  • Tests updates of Deikto counters, SwatTest#testDeiktoLimits().
  • Tests for relationship editor, SwatTest#testRelationshipEditor().
  • Tests for relationship settings editor, SwatTest#testRelationshipSettings().
  • Tests for scriptalyzer, SwatTest#testScriptalyzer().
  • Tests for the state stack of verb editor, SwatTest#testVerbEditorStateStack().
  • Tests for relationship window of storyteller, SwatTest#testStorytellerRelationshipsWindow().
  • Test for trivial momentous slider, SwatTest#testVerbPropertiesEditor().
  • Tests adding, renaming and deleting verbs, SwatTest#testVerbEditing().
  • Tests for statistics, UnitTests#testStatistics().
